description: The Emerald is an exquisite luxury high-rise building, just one block from Pike Place Market and two from the newly transformed Seattle Waterfront. This thoughtfully designed residence features floor-to-ceiling windows with waterfront views, White Oak hardwoods, custom wood cabinets, Carrara marble counter tops, Bosch appliances, a spacious, spa-like bath, full-size washer/dryer, custom shades, and Latch keyless entry. The den/office offers potential as a non-conforming 2nd bedroom. Enjoy premier amenities: 24hr concierge, fitness center, yoga studio, pet run, guest suite, onsite electric carshare, and a stunning indoor/outdoor rooftop lounge with panoramic views of Elliott Bay, Mt. Rainier, and the Olympics that will leave you captivated!
